# ==========================================
# PhonTracer .gitignore (Whitelist Approach)
# ==========================================

# 1. 默认忽略所有文件和文件夹
*

# 2. 允许 Git 遍历所有目录结构（否则无法到达深层文件）
!*/

# 3. 白名单：必须保留的核心根目录文件
!.gitignore
!README.md
!README_REVISION_GUIDE.md
!PAPER_USAGE_GUIDE.md
!requirements.txt
!requirements-phonrec-engine.txt
!main.py
!cli.py
!toolkit.py
!ToneExtractor.spec
!ToneExtractor_Suite.spec
!installer.iss

# 4. 白名单：核心代码与资源目录
!modules/**
!assets/**
!tests/**
!.github/**
!工作流/Toolkit脚本/**
!PhonAcq V4.9/Canary.py
!PhonAcq V4.9/requirements.txt
!PhonAcq V4.9/phonacq_lite/**

# 5. [已移除 example/ 白名单]

# 6. 强制排除：即使在白名单目录内也绝对不跟踪的东西
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.so
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
.DS_Store
desktop.ini
assets/manual/manual_2026-05-25_to_2026-05-30_supplement.md
assets/manual/manual_2026-06-01_to_2026-06-13_supplement.md

# 7. 排除本地环境与构建产物
.venv/
env/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
.vscode/
.idea/
build/
dist/
dist_new/
scratch/
upx.exe
upx.zip
upx-*/

# 8. 绝对排除实验文件夹
Test/

# 9. 本地打包与测试输出文件夹
Cli_test/
!modules/formant_optimizer.py

# 10. PhonRec Recording Suite Whitelist
!PhonRec/backend/main.py
!PhonRec/backend/test_backend.py
!PhonRec/frontend/**
PhonRec/frontend/node_modules/
PhonRec/frontend/dist/
PhonRec/frontend/dist-electron/
PhonRec/frontend/src-tauri/target/
PhonRec/frontend/eslint_errors.txt
PhonRec/backend/workspace/
PhonRec/backend/__pycache__/
